computing can be seen as a form of rental business With improving virtualization technology, it became possible to integrate the IT resources located in different spaces into a single svstem for service long','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:01','2025-04-19 12:45:01'),(3057,'907','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','Cloud computing has a direct and interactive relationship with the IT sector, which encompasses networks, hardware, solutions, and applications The stakeholders of cloud computing can be divided into three main groups. In the first group are vendors who provide hardware, solutions, and applications to cloud service providers. In the second group are providers that provide cloud services to users and some global leading companies are Amazon, sales force dotcom, and Google. Third, there are various users such as individual users or corporate users, those that actually use cloud services. Users can rent as much services as need and can scale up their services in real-time in response to increased service loads, support real-time scalability based on service load. And only have to pay as  L they they they .','',3,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:01','2025-04-19 12:45:01'),(3058,'907','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','10 Cloud services are made up of the following technologies. Cloud client is a technology for utilizing cloud computing services like cloud lightweight terminal platform technology, cloud-mobile technology, and cloud agents Cloud service and applications are technologies for providing the many types of cloud computing services in SW or application format Cloud platform is a cloud computing technology for providing in service format, the platform of basic functions for easily developing services Cloud infrastructure is a cloud technology that provides resources such as servers, storage, ad networks as services to users. push','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:01','2025-04-19 12:45:01'),(3059,'696','App\\Models\\Section','Text','Global loT is presently in 