rs can provide include information services using augmented reality, services that help drivers by recognizing and notifying them about road conditions ahead, and fully autonomous driving and automatic parking that do not require any driver response.','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:01','2025-04-19 12:45:01'),(3092,'916','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'<Table81  Teaching method and tools for smart education',NULL,'68039aefc7005.png','/storage/tables/68039aefc7005.png','2025-04-19 12:45:01','2025-04-19 12:45:35'),(3093,'916','App\\Models\\Subsection','Figures',NULL,'[Fig.72] Concept of smart education',NULL,'68039aefe114a.png','/storage/figures/68039aefe114a.png','2025-04-19 12:45:01','2025-04-19 12:45:35'),(3094,'916','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','Among the social changes brought about by advanced digital environment, the changes that could affect the education environment are the increased number of couples who decide to live together without tying the knot, the continuously declining birth rate, the arrival of an age When individual choices are respected, and the rapid aging of the population To respond to these societal changes, the government established a national strategy on smart education with a basic plan on informatization of education in the country: along','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:01','2025-04-19 12:45:01'),(3095,'916','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','The government\'s smart education program produced a digital textbook prototype in 2006, based on basic research that began in 1997. In 2007, the Ministry of Education developed digital textbooks for the teaching of Korean, English and mathematics and discussed the commercial rollout. After that the ministry announced the \"Smart Educatior Promotion Strategy\" in 2011 and is presently pursuing a smart education program under a new set of policies Together with the digital textbook, smart classroom is the other important pillar of smart education Smart classroom is a new way of teachin