ssues','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3164,'63','App\\Models\\Module','Text','The development of IT technology is causing fluctuations in all industries in the modern society, maximizing the convenience and efficiency of modern life In particular, the services created by IT technology are being developed to operate prioritizing the user\'s convenience and interests, but as the enhanced software intelligence and increases the side effects and risks of misuse, abuse, and malicious use. The importance of ethical responsibility is also increasing: Against this backdrop, it is necessary to understand the professional ethics of IT business-related developers. rapid','',2,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3165,'63','App\\Models\\Module','Header','Learning Objectives:','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3166,'63','App\\Models\\Module','Text','1. To be able to describe the professional ethics of IT business workers 2 To be able to explain the principles ad codes of professional ethics related to IT business','',4,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3167,'63','App\\Models\\Module','Header','Keywords:','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3168,'63','App\\Models\\Module','Text','Professional Ethics, Ethics, Work Ethics, Community Ethics, Ethics and Law','',6,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3169,'63','App\\Models\\Module','Header','Preview for practical business','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3170,'63','App\\Models\\Module','Text','In March 2018, a group of people who leaked the design drawings of a domestic front-load washing machine motor to China was caught by the police It turned out that they handed over the motor drawings for the front-load washing machine developed by a domestic company through tens of billions of won in investment over 10 years, in return for KRW 60 million in cash, housing, and vehicles According to the Gyeongnam Provincial Police Agencys International Crime Investigation Unit, two people were arrested on charges of violating the law on the prevention of unfair competition and protection of trade secrets, and three other people who assisted them with the leakage were arrested. Among them, Mr: A is alleged to have moved to a Chinese company with a laptop in which the design drawings and technical data related to manufacturing of the entire product line are stored, while serving as the research head of a Chinese local subsidiary of a medium-sized company in Gwangju that manufactures and produces high-efficiency motors for front-load washing machines in January 2015. Moreover, Mr B, who served as a researcher in the production technology department of the same company, secretly took away 5918 related files such as design drawings and inspection data for production facilities when he resigned in February 2015. In addition, three other people who worked for the same company are also suspected of stealing design drawings of production facilities and transferring them to Mr key In March 2018, group of people who leaked the design drawings of a domestic front-load washing machine motor to China was caught by the police It turned out that handed over the motor drawings for the front-load washing machine developed by a domestic company through tens of billions of won in investment over 10 years in return for KRW 60 million in cash, housing, and vehicles they According to the Gyeongnam Provincial Police Agency\'s Interational Crime Investigation Unit, two people were arrested on charges of violating the law on the prevention of unfair competition and protection of trade secrets, and three other people who assisted them with the leakage were arrested. In response, Tae-hee Lee, Sergeant of the GimhaeJungbu Police Station s investigation department, said, While technology and systems have been highly developed and improved over time, there are still some that remain outdated It is professional ethics,\" explaining that the fundamental cause of safety accidents is,in the end, an individual without a proper sense of professional ethics things [Source] Etoday, Yonhap News, SBS, Maeil Business News Korea, Gyeongnam Daily Newspaper 2018-03-','',2,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3171,'929','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'',NULL,'68039af385bd7.png','/storage/tables/68039af385bd7.png','2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:39'),(3172,'929','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','job. Many people in modern society engage in vocational activities while belonging to a specific organization called the workplace, not only attaining self-realization but also forming relationships and interacting with others while participating in the common life of society: At this time, the norms and standards that can be applied to individuals\' mindsets, attitudes and related behaviors toward jobs and work, and mutual relations required in a specific setting of a job can be called professional ethics In the normative aspect, professional ethics consists of ethical norms that must be observed among people in their professional life, norms made up of rules of common behavior, and norms that limit harmful behaviors that should not be performed, that is, unethical behaviors','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3173,'930','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'<Table 96  Checklist for Professional Ethics?s',NULL,'68039af3accba.png','/storage/tables/68039af3accba.png','2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:39'),(3174,'930','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'',NULL,'68039af3ca40d.png','/storage/tables/68039af3ca40d.png','2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:39'),(3175,'930','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'<Table 97  Answer Checklist',NULL,'68039af3db53f.png','/storage/tables/68039af3db53f.png','2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:39'),(3176,'930','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','Professional ethics is necessary for responsibilities ad duties as a professional while realizing one s self based on moral values, and is a requirement that must be met for cooperation in a community life pursuing common fulfilling Tiuicssiuniai Cli iic) 1) iicesjaiy iui 141s \'Cspuiisidiiilic) aliu uulics 05 a pruiessiuniai WviC iCaiilins Uiic ) #ci based on moral values, and is a requirement that must be met for cooperation in a community life pursuing common interests, The reason professional ethics is important is that the vocational activities have a significant influence on the order ad development of companies and society as a whole, beyond the individual level Like the saying, \"Ethics rather than makes a company of 200 years, ethics is an important factor that ensures reliability and leads to competitiveness in economic activities If the level of professional ethics is low, individuals only prioritize their own interests and not be considerate of others. In addition, cooperation and interaction necessary for professional life not be achieved well, and profit will may 24 Human Resources Development Service of Korea, NCS National Competency Standard Occupational Ethics Workbook 2016','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3177,'930','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','furthermore, the credibility of the organization related to the profession may be lacking and the order of society may be destroyed. This may be directly linked the matter of national competitiveness and economic development: Therefore, professional ethics is necessary for the individual as a professional and also for the reliability of the company, the order and development of society, and the development of the profession itself The following is a checklist for self-identification of the level of professional ethics generally required of all professionals Think about your usual behavior check what matches your behavior','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3178,'930','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','5 Human Resources Development Service of Korea, NCS National Competency Standard Occupational Ethics Workbook, 2016','',3,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3179,'930','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','Count and write down the number of each item the table below, and take note of the items checked with \'Disagree\". using','',2,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:05','2025-04-19 12:45:05'),(3180,'931','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','Professional ethics can be divided into two. One is general ethics required of any professional, and the other is special ethics of a specific profession IT business is developing rapidly as various technologies compete with other and form a huge ecosystem, and are directly affecting the quality of life of everyone throughout the world. However, safety accidents, information security accidents, and cyber-crimes frequently appear due to the lack of professional ethics of ICT industry workers and software developers. As the negative impact of such accidents expands and social losses increase, the need and importance of professional ethics of IT business workers is emphasized There is no global standard of professional ethics encompassing the entire IT business. However, you can look up the norms that are considered important in IT business in the internal code of conduct of individual professional organizations or companies Examples are the ACM (Association for Computing Machinery) Code of Ethics and Professional Conduct,, IEEE- CS(Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers Computer Science)Software Engineering Code, and NSPE(National Society of Professional Engineers) Code of Ethics for Engineers Codes of ethics commonly found in these codes are required more as the intelligent information societys dependence on IT technology increases include moral responsibility for safety and the implementation of technology each being They public','',1,NULL,NU