 license number) Name (including Chinese/English name, pen name, etc ) Detailed address (address included up to the district(gu) unit) Date information: birthday (yangllunar calendar), anniversary (marriage, first birthday, sixtieth birthday, etc ) , date of certificate, etc, Phone number (mobile phone number, home phone number, company phone number, fax number) Medical record number, health insurance number welfare recipient number Account number, credit card number Various qualifications and license numbers Vehicle number, registration number & serial number of various devices Photos (still photos, videos, CCTV footage, etc ) Body identification information (fingerprint, voice, iris, etc) Email address, IP address, Mac address, homepage URL, etc Identification code (ID, employee number, customer number, etc ) Other unique identification number: serial number business registration number of sole military = Methods of De-identification: A range of methods including pseudonymization, aggregation, data suppression and data masking can be used individually or in combination. There are various kinds of technology in place to realize each method. The most suitable methods and specific techniques need to be chosen and utilized based on the purpose of data usage, and strengths and weaknesses of each method.','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:09','2025-04-19 12:45:09'),(3246,'716','App\\Models\\Section','Figures',NULL,'',NULL,'68039af749611.png','/storage/figures/68039af749611.png','2025-04-19 12:45:09','2025-04-19 12:45:43'),(3247,'716','App\\Models\\Section','Figures',NULL,'',NULL,'68039af762231.png','/storage/figures/68039af762231.png','2025-04-19 12:45:09','2025-04-19 12:45:43'),(3248,'716','App\\Models\\Section','Text','<Example  Application of non-identification measure','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:09','2025-04-19 12:45:09'),(3249,'947','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'<Table 102  Criteria for obligated persons',NULL,'68039af77eea7.png','/storage/tables/68