come a global trend, serves as a growth engine of Korea Personal information protection becomes an important issue in industries. The signing of FTAs with countries around the world has increased cross-border exchange of personal information Personal information issues affect public administration credibility and national brand','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:09','2025-04-19 12:45:09'),(3258,'65','App\\Models\\Module','Header','Recent Trends and Major Issues','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:11','2025-04-19 12:45:11'),(3259,'65','App\\Models\\Module','Text','Intellectual property rights consist of all property rights arising from intellectual activities, industrial property rights for the purpose of industrial development,, and copyrights for the purpose of cultural development With recent economic, social, or cultural changes or the development of science ad technology, various intellectual properties are also emerging in new fields. Intellectual property is an important corporate asset, and the transaction of intellectual property is exploding Therefore, by learning about intellectual property rights that you must know while working in the IT business field, you can understand the importance of intellectual property protection','',2,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:11','2025-04-19 12:45:11'),(3260,'65','App\\Models\\Module','Header','Learning Objectives','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:11','2025-04-19 12:45:11'),(3261,'65','App\\Models\\Module','Text','1. To be able to explain about copyrights and copyrights infringement prevention 2 To be able to explain intellectual property rights and industrial property rights','',4,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:11','2025-04-19 12:45:11'),(3262,'65','App\\Models\\Module','Header','Keywords','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-19 12:45:11','2025-04-19 12:45:11'),(3263,'65','App\\Models\\Module','Text','Intellectual property rights, copyrights, authors rights, industrial property rights, new intellectual property rights, business works